{"parentUuid":"2593f8bc-10ca-4ec7-93ff-e9338f79fadb","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/hukaikun/Desktop/kevin in UIUC/CS124/124 project","sessionId":"2921527a-dd0a-46d6-aea3-e96cc4f15450","version":"2.1.72","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"cozy-exploring-crayon","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01TnT4JDWV9BG46NuD15HXWd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这是一个 Android 项目，但当前目录下还没有项目文件（只有 `.idea` 配置目录）。\n\n要启动 Android 模拟器，有以下几种方式：\n\n**方式 1：通过 Android Studio（推荐）**\n1. 打开 Android Studio\n2. 点击工具栏的 **Device Manager**（设备管理器）图标\n3. 在列表中找到你的虚拟设备，点击右侧的 ▶ 运行按钮\n\n**方式 2：通过命令行**\n```bash\n# 列出可用的虚拟设备\n~/Library/Android/sdk/emulator/emulator -list-avds\n\n# 启动某个设备（替换 <AVD_NAME>）\n~/Library/Android/sdk/emulator/emulator -avd <AVD_NAME>\n```\n\n**方式 3：通过 Android Studio 顶部工具栏**\n1. 在设备选择下拉菜单中选择一个模拟器\n2. 点击绿色运行按钮 ▶\n\n---\n\n另外，你的项目目录目前只有 `.idea` 文件夹，没有实际的源代码文件。你是否需要先创建或导入项目？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":307,"cache_read_input_tokens":13941,"output_tokens":354,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":307,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYuxffL5w6rGzwQK9BiAL","type":"assistant","uuid":"78949f04-9d69-467c-a27e-d964cdc6077b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T19:35:13.404Z"}
